Orascom Construction Raised to ‘Buy’ at Deutsche Bank on Prices

-- B y   Z a i n a b   F a t t a h
-- 
2011-09-28T05:12:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/orascom-construction-raised-to-buy-at-deutsche-bank-on-prices.html
Orascom Construction Industries,
 Egypt ’s biggest publicly traded builder, was raised to “buy”
from “hold” at Deutsche Bank AG, citing higher fertilizer
prices and expectations of new contracts.  The share-price estimate was raised to 270 Egyptian pounds
from 250 pounds, the bank said in a note to clients dated today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
